Defining Well-Known Uniform Resource
Identifiers (URIs)
2010", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC5785.html", target="_top", tooltip="This memo defines a path prefix for well-known locations, /.well-known/, in selected Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) schemes. [STANDARDS-TRACK]"];
